reviewText: Fantastic, I don't understand why networks don't produce series like this all the time.  No foul words in the whole series!!

Best series broadcast on USA or any other network.
Well written full of humor with excellent character development. And Matt Bomer is also easy on the eyes.
The only series I have purchased for myself and which I watch over and over again!

This series is amazing :D
I love the condition and speed at which I received the DVDs, Thank You!!!!
Love this series. Well worth the price. Nice to watch at my convenience.
